; Test N directive (nomarket_directive) (lines 131-138 of textual_directives.cc)
; Exercise the N line which marks a commodity as nomarket

N MYSTOCK

2024/01/01 Test
    Assets:Investments    10 MYSTOCK
    Assets:Cash          $-1000.00

test reg
24-Jan-01 Test                  Assets:Investments       10 MYSTOCK   10 MYSTOCK
                                Assets:Cash               $-1000.00    $-1000.00
                                                                      10 MYSTOCK
end test
